# requirements: up_down_counter
# extracted from: counter.intent
# NOTE: Never overwritten by pssgen.

[SYS-REQ-001] Counter shall support active-low reset.
  verification: simulation

[FUNC-REQ-002] Counter shall count up and down.
  verification: simulation, post-silicon

[FUNC-REQ-003] Count output shall roll over correctly.
  verification: simulation

[PERF-REQ-004] Reset response within one clock cycle.
  verification: post-silicon
  [WAIVED] Cannot verify sub-cycle timing pre-silicon.
